{"word":"H7599 - שָׁאַן - shâʼan - shaw-an' - Be at ease","slug":"H7599","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁאַן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>shâʼan"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>shaw-an'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Be at ease"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D0;&#x05DF; - sha&#x0302;'an</b> - <i>shaw-an'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>loll</i>, that is, <i>be peaceful</i>: - be at ease, be quiet, rest. See also <a href=\"#/H1052\">H1052</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7600\">H7600</a>"}]}